    {
      "id": "9ae8f957-f198-4473-9d64-0927318c6fc6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "To address the limitation, authors propose Diagnostic Transformer, a new arquitecture that goes from question-level to knowledge level. In other works, the model diagnoses the learner’s knowledge from question mastery states. Th new training paradigm also focuses on stability of knowledge state diagnosis. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "9ae8f957-f198-4473-9d64-0927318c6fc6",
        "parent": {
